article_id:1138,category_name:Events,title_name:A Raid Event Revival, Skyborne Spectacle, Is Coming Soon!,image_path:https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/3ad4f173f770e116f48150d16e3aa279.png,message:<div>The Skyborne Spectacle raid event revival will begin <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1583992800"></span>!</div><div><br></div><div>During this event, you can use co-op play to fight against the water-attuned raid boss.</div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/3ad4f173f770e116f48150d16e3aa279.png"></div><div>The prince and his friends have come to a town that will be celebrating the Lunar New Year. There&#39;ll be food, dragon dances, and even spectacular pyroblossoms at night... But danger arises suddenly amidst preparations for the event! A young practitioner of kung fu, a brave wanderer, and a panda dragon will rise up to face a mighty enemy who&#39;s disrupting the flow of mana!<br><br>â– Notes<br>1. Players must have completed up to Chapter 2 / 2-1 (Normal) of the main campaign to participate in event quests.<br>2. Players must have completed up to Chapter 2 / 2-1 (Normal) of the main campaign in order to play co-op.<br><br>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1583906400,update_time1583465012